When Andrej says "This is a very serious production-grade system. It is trained on a good chunk of the internet, and then there's a lot of pre-training and fine-tuning stages to it," he is explaining that ChatGPT, the AI system in focus, is not a simple model. It is an advanced, highly developed system that has been trained on substantial amounts of data from the internet, and has undergone significant pre-training and fine-tuning to refine its capabilities.